reviews.review_text: what else can be said absolutley, unequivocally righteous sounding tape. it's alive, electric tangible brilliance ... are you not entertained? Thank y'all so much for the care and love that went into this, it's more than amazing. It's the Grateful Dead. * Nick 12/26/2022
